{"id": "art-507", "label": "Art. 507", "title": "Art. 507: Exercitarea autorităţii părinteşti de către un singur părinte", "slug": "art-507", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1378851724\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1139\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1378851724\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 507:\nExercitarea autorit&#259;&#355;ii p&#259;rinte&#351;ti de c&#259;tre un singur\np&#259;rinte </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_230569604\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1138\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_230569604\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Dac&#259; unul dintre p&#259;rin&#355;i este decedat,\ndeclarat mort prin hot&#259;râre judec&#259;toreasc&#259;, beneficiaz&#259; de\ntutel&#259; special&#259;, este dec&#259;zut din exerci&#355;iul drepturilor\np&#259;rinte&#351;ti sau dac&#259;, din orice motiv, se afl&#259; în\nneputin&#355;&#259; de a-&#351;i exprima voin&#355;a, cel&#259;lalt\np&#259;rinte exercit&#259; singur autoritatea p&#259;rinteasc&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2088006423\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1137\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2088006423\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)P&#259;rintele cu privire la care a fost instituit&#259;\ntutela special&#259; p&#259;streaz&#259; dreptul de a veghea asupra modului de\ncre&#351;tere &#351;i educare a copilului, precum &#351;i dreptul de a\nconsim&#355;i la adop&#355;ia acestuia, cu excep&#355;ia cazului în care se\nafl&#259; în imposibilitatea de a-&#351;i manifesta voin&#355;a din cauza\nlipsei discern&#259;mântului.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>CAPITOLUL IV:Dec&#259;derea din\nexerci&#355;iul drepturilor p&#259;rinte&#351;ti</span></b></p>"}